    {
        "content": "<p>In mathlib, we use <code>bool</code> instead of <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\{\\pm 1\\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">±</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">}</span></span></span></span> just for convenience.</p>",
